The '''Makkah Chamber of Commerce & Industry''' ('''MCCI''') is a semi-government organization that regulates and serves the business community in [[Makkah Region|Makkah]]. The MCCI was established by a royal decree dated January 1947.<ref>https://twitter.com/MakkahChamber?lang=en</ref>

The MCCI opened their own building in 2013.<ref>https://www.alarabiya.net/articles/2013/01/23/262144.html</ref>

